headline: Martin Marietta Materials (MLM) Surged Following an Asset Swap Deal
summary: TimesSquare Capital Management, an equity investment management company, released its “U.S. Focus Growth Strategy” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, all the major asset classes posted positive returns except fixed income assets outside the US.
